name: Pokeball Premierball #14 | GLB 3D
description: A Premier Ball is a type of Poké Ball introduced in the third generation. It acts the same way as a regular Poké Ball but have a completely white design and are given as a gift when ten or more Poké Balls are bought at once. However, buying 20 or more in a single purchase only yields only one so, to get more, the player must do multiple transactions.
